			Company Description 


			Pier 1 Imports, Inc. is engaged in providing retail sales of decorative home furnishings, furniture and gifts. Its products include decorative home furnishings, dining, kitchen goods, bath, bedding accessories, and specialty items for the home. The company was founded in 1962 and is headquartered in...
		


                Pier 1 Imports, Inc. is engaged in providing retail sales of decorative home furnishings, furniture and gifts. Its products include decorative home furnishings, dining, kitchen goods, bath, bedding accessories, and specialty items for the home. The company was founded in 1962 and is headquartered in Fort Worth, TX.
            




