  Pier 1 Imports, Inc., (NYSE:PIR) a leading retailer of exclusive home décor and furniture, is pleased to announce it is now offering a new line of rugs and pillows from Magnolia Home by Joanna Gaines, co-owner, co-founder and lead designer of Magnolia. The assortment is now available on pier1.com and will arrive in stores on April 17, 2017.  "We are delighted to bring this remarkable collection from Magnolia Home to Pier 1 Imports," said Cathy David, Executive Vice President of Merchandising for Pier 1 Imports. "We hope this assortment of plush, durable fabrics and rustic wool blends will continue to inspire our customers to discover endless possibilities for their home," said Ms. David.  The assortment includes more than 40 rugs and pillows in store, with more than 110 additional styles and size extensions available online. The versatile pieces are functional and beautiful - allowing customers to create a space that reflects their own character.  Each pillow and rug was inspired by Ms. Gaines' simple and fresh style. The esteemed, influential designer partnered with Loloi, an award winning rug and pillow manufacturer, to create the assortment. Every texture, design and color was thoughtfully selected resulting in a timeless collection.  About Pier 1 Imports  Pier 1 Imports is dedicated to offering customers exclusive, one-of-a-kind products that reflect high quality at a great value. Starting with a single store in 1962, Pier 1 Imports' products are now available in retail stores throughout the U.S. and Canada and online at pier1.com. For more information about Pier 1 Imports or to find the nearest store, please visit pier1.com.  



 








 










































